---
layout: base.njk
title: L'Archive / Dossiers
description: Forgotten Industries dossier records and continuity packets.
permalink: /archive/projects/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">L'Archive / Dossiers</p>
    <h1>Dossiers</h1>
    <p class="tagline">
      Dossiers and continuity packets for long-running systems, restorations,
      object groups, and recovery work.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="evidence-band">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">{{ archive.projects | count }} records</p>
      <h2>Dossiers keep the archive coherent.</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="link-list archive-record-list">
      {% for project in archive.projects %}
      <li id="{{ project.id }}">
        <p class="entry-note">
          {{ project.id }} / {{ project.category }} / {{ project.status }}
        </p>
        <h3><a href="{{ project | archiveProjectUrl }}">{{ project.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ project.summary }}</p>
        {% if project.working_title %}
        <p class="entry-note">{{ project.working_title }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Browse</p>
      <h2>Dossiers by taxonomy.</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="link-list">
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/archive/objects/">Objects and components</a></h3>
        <p>Inventory records grouped into crawlable object pages.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/archive/systems/">Systems</a></h3>
        <p>Field systems, restoration systems, and project contexts.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/archive/status/">Status</a></h3>
        <p>Browse by restoration, custody, test, and evidence state.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
